description:
During the tightened quarantine regime in Baku, Sumgayit, Ganja, Lankaran, Yevlakh, Masalli, Jalilabad, Mingachevir, Goranboy, Goygol cities and Absheron, Barda, Samukh, Siyazan, Sheki, Khachmaz regions, public transportation will be suspended in following dates and times:

From 00:00 on July 4, 2020 to 06:00 on July 6, 2020;
From 00:00 on July 11, 2020 to 06:00 on July 13, 2020; 
From 00:00 on July 18, 2020 to 06:00 on July 20, 2020.
